data.description: Step inside this beautiful 5 BR and 2.5 Bath home that will accommodate all of your needs. A versatile shed with electricity awaits in the backyard, ideal for hobbies or storage. Entertainment options abound with a fantastic Finished Room Over Garage (FROG), complete with a built-in movie screen and projector – included with the property. Movie nights and gaming sessions just got an upgrade! The master bathroom has been tastefully remodeled, adding a touch of luxury. Fresh paint throughout the house brightens every room, while beautiful hardwood graces the upper level. Outside, a charming fenced backyard beckons, complete with a fire pit for cozy gatherings. This space is perfect for relaxation and entertaining. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Portsmouth gem your own. Schedule a viewing today to explore all the possibilities!
